{"type":null,"faqId":8828,"title":"荣耀3X（G750-T00） 照相/摄像文件默认保存路径和更改方法","answer":"<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span><span><span>G750</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中照相机的拍摄文件会优先存储在</span><span><span>SD</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡中，如果手机中未插入</span><span><span>SD</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡，则会默认保存到手机内部存储。当用户插入</span><span><span>SD</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡后，默认就会存储到</span><span><span>SD</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡上，不需要用户手动更改（该存储位置不受设置里面的默认存储位置影响），如需更换保存路径可通过如下的方法：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span></span><span><span><span>1、</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">相机</span><span><span>-&gt;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span><span><span>-&gt;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">优先保存位置，如下图所示：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29289\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-15.95pt;\">\n\t<span><span><span>2</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、2、在优先保存位置中可以切换</span><span><span>SD</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡或者内部存储，如下图所示：</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-15.95pt;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp; <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29295\" />&nbsp;</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-15.95pt;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;当存储位置为手机存储时，照相机的存储路径为文件管理：内部存储</span><span><span>\\DCIM\\Camera</span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:0cm;\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当存储位置为</span><span><span>SD</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡时，照相机的存储路径为文件管理：</span><span><span>SD</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡</span><span><span>\\DCIM\\Camera</span></span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9409","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396081775000,"seriesProductName":"G750-T00","visitedTimes":1647,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}